  questions:
  - question: "\xC7ocuk odas\u0131nda deprem s\u0131ras\u0131nda hangi e\u015Fya
      tehlikeli olabilir?"
    answers:
    - "Hal\u0131"
    - "Sabitlenmemi\u015F dolap"
    - "Yast\u0131k"
    - Defter
    correctIndex: 1
  - question: "Deprem \xE7antas\u0131 nerede bulunmal\u0131d\u0131r?"
    answers:
    - "Ula\u015F\u0131lmas\u0131 zor yerde"
    - Kilitli dolapta
    - "Kolay ula\u015F\u0131labilir yerde"
    - "Balkon d\u0131\u015F\u0131nda"
    correctIndex: 2
  - question: "Deprem s\u0131ras\u0131nda oyuncak toplamak neden yanl\u0131\u015Ft\u0131r?"
    answers:
    - "Zaman kaybettirdi\u011Fi i\xE7in"
    - "Oyuncaklar a\u011F\u0131r oldu\u011Fu i\xE7in"
    - "Oyun bozuldu\u011Fu i\xE7in"
    - "G\xFCr\xFClt\xFC yapt\u0131\u011F\u0131 i\xE7in"
